            <p class="mb-4">4.1 You can cancel your order up to 14 days after your order is delivered. But you have to give a proper reason for cancelling. This period allows you a conditional right to cancel.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">4.2 How to cancel: Simply email us at support@coursecave.org or call us +440203 289 8484 with your order details to cancel your order.</p>
